# sprint — release notes

## When to invoke

The user wants user-facing or internal release notes for what shipped.

## Steps

1. Group changes: **New**, **Improved**, **Fixed**, **Known issues** as appropriate.
2. Write for the **audience** (end users vs operators) — one primary reader.
3. Link to docs, tickets, or commits when helpful.
4. Save as `docs/` or `CHANGELOG` per team convention.
